</div>
</div>
<div class="thumb tright">
<div class="thumbinner" style="width:222px;"><a href="/wiki/File:Aareschlaufe_Bern-East.svg" class="image"><img alt="" src="//upload.wikimedia.org/wikipedia/commons/thumb/0/0d/Aareschlaufe_Bern-East.svg/220px-Aareschlaufe_Bern-East.svg.png" width="220" height="171" class="thumbimage" srcset="//upload.wikimedia.org/wikipedia/commons/thumb/0/0d/Aareschlaufe_Bern-East.svg/330px-Aareschlaufe_Bern-East.svg.png 1.5x, //upload.wikimedia.org/wikipedia/commons/thumb/0/0d/Aareschlaufe_Bern-East.svg/440px-Aareschlaufe_Bern-East.svg.png 2x" data-file-width="2453" data-file-height="1908" /></a>
